title: As world seeks to eradicate polio, Laos suffers vaccine-linked case
text:
Published By: Reuters - Health - Today 
GENEVA/LONDON (Reuters) - Laos has suffered a case of vaccine-derived polio, the World Health Organization said on Monday, in a new setback ...
